    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248110/extras/d2d6eb130ed090956d6e9ea57442c5c9.avif?t=1770110413\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248110/extras_big/d2d6eb130ed090956d6e9ea57442c5c9.avif?t=1770110413 width=800 height=128 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >这是一款围绕“凑十”展开的禅意肉鸽卡牌构筑游戏。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的目标很简单：操纵多种“易术”，将场上的数字牌凑成10的倍数，触发华丽的连锁反应，感受“规划—收获”的纯粹心流体验。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>打造你的专属构筑</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>6枚符文 + 7种易术 + 100多个灵石 = 变化莫测的策略组合</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从6枚风格迥异的【符文】中择一作为你的构筑核心：是选择【风】符，在急速决策中获得豪爽奖励？还是选择【木】符，稳扎稳打，厚积薄发？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >活用【易术】改写牌面，再用上百种效果各异的【灵石】塑造你的策略。叠加、组合、触发连锁，探索并打磨出属于你的拿手流派。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>充满变数</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随机生成的手牌与商店</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【挥汗模式】冲击规则的随机挑战</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>禅意之境</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简约柔和的视觉设计，原创的舒缓背景音乐，助你沉浸于「归拾」之境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248110/extras/0be4341a2c739cd134d0656aa7da7194.avif?t=1770110413\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248110/extras_big/0be4341a2c739cd134d0656aa7da7194.avif?t=1770110413 width=800 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>立即将《归拾》加入愿望单，开启一场牌与策略的禅意之旅！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248110/extras/1f2984b0e61dd5d9d8e8bb9aca618ef7.webp?t=1770110413\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248110/extras_big/1f2984b0e61dd5d9d8e8bb9aca618ef7.webp?t=1770110413 width=800 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >正式版内容</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 6枚符文</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 7种易术</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 100+个灵石</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 20个关卡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 完整的挥汗模式挑战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >试玩版内容</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 2枚符文</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 4种易术</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 70+个灵石</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 13个关卡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 部分挥汗模式挑战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >温馨提示</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 【试玩版】的存档为本地独立存档，未来购买正式版后，将开启一段全新的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 我们仍在努力打磨和优化游戏，游戏的内容可能会随开发进度调整，感谢您的理解！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
